Sriracha Turkey Burger

25 min
$12.5
350 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

GlutenDairy

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinLow Carb

Cuisine:

Description

Juicy turkey burger with a spicy kick from sriracha, topped with fresh veggies.

Ingredients

  • ground turkey: 1 lb
  • burger buns: 4
  • sriracha sauce: 3 tbsp
  • lettuce: 4 leaves
  • tomato: 1, sliced
  • red onion: 1, sliced
  • cheddar cheese: 4 slices
  • olive oil: 1 tbsp
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
